my personal take at the flight problem presented in a video. 
problem from: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qz9tKlF431k&ab_channel=Cl%C3%A9mentMihailescu
task:
  connect a new theoreical eirport to an existing network of flights
conditions:
  set up little new flighst as possible
  the new airport has to be onected with all other airports 
  the number of layovers in order to connect new airport is not limited

the script is work in porgress
